---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="The Book — DragonCraft" locale="en">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Narrative Engine</h1>
    <p>Content Operating System in the AI Era · 22 Chapters</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-content">

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Part 1: Foundations (Intro ~ C03)</h2>
      <div class="chapter-list">

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">Intro</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Narrative Equality</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Great storytelling isn't a talent — it's a learnable底层能力. In the AI era, this skill matters more than ever, and is easier for more people to master.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T130519==z--引子__intro__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C01</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Narrative Instinct: Why Humans Are Born Storytellers</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">You scroll past a video. But when you hear a story, you stop. You want to hear more — that's the raw power of narrative.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201739==z--叙事本能__chapter01__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C02</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Eight-Blade Method: How to Dissect Any Narrative</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Historical · Dialectical · Phenomenological · Linguistic · Formal · Existential · Aesthetic · Meta-reflective — eight blades to cut any story open and see its structure.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T150835==z--八刀解剖法__chapter03__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C03</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Personal IP: Turn Your Experience Into an Asset</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Most people think Personal IP is about "telling your story." It's actually about "designing your story." Same experience, different telling — completely different effect.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T152339==z--个人IP__chapter04__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Part 2: Scenario Skills (C04 ~ C14 + C14 + C15)</h2>
      <div class="chapter-list">

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C04</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Brand Storytelling: Make Users主动认同"Who You Are"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Products can be copied. Features can be surpassed. But your brand story is an asset that can't be bought — if you tell it right.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T152919==z--品牌叙事__chapter05__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C05</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Product Launch: Make Audiences Want to Order Immediately</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Another product launch ended. You closed the stream — and immediately wanted to buy. That's not the product. That's narrative rhythm, precisely designed.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T153542==z--产品发布__chapter06__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C06</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Startup Funding: Make Investors Believe "It's Got to Be You"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Your BP has market size and business model. What investors actually fund is whether the story you're telling is credible.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T153825==z--创业融资__chapter07__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C07</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Sales Persuasion: From "Let Me Think About It" to "I'm In"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">You know every feature by heart. The customer听完says "Let me think about it." You're not telling a story — you're reciting specs.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T190641==z--销售说服__chapter08__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C08</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Organizational Change: Get Employees to Embrace the New Strategy</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">The CEO is passionate on stage. Employees are thinking "here we go again." The strategy is fine — the telling is broken.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T191402==z--组织变革__chapter09__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C09</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Charity & Fundraising: Make Donors Feel "This Is About Me"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">"XX children starve every day" — numbers like this numb people. Great fundraising narrative makes people feel their participation actually changes something.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T193857==z--公益筹款__chapter10__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C10</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Social Media: 3-Second Hook + 45-Second Expansion + Closing Quote</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">You wrote what you thought was great content — 300 views. You wrote a story — 30,000 views. The difference isn't the content. It's the structure.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T194441==z--社交媒体__chapter11__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C11</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Education: 3 Minutes to Pull Learners Into a New World</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Students walk in thinking about work, spreadsheets, what's for dinner. A great opening narrative pulls their attention into another world in 3 minutes.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201918==z--教育开场__chapter12__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C12</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Crisis PR: The 4A Model Turns "Accident" Into "Story"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">The crisis is escalating. Your CEO is pushing, your legal team is blocking, your PR is drafting statements. The 4A model gives crisis narrative a path forward.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201918==z--公关危机__chapter13__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C13</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Exploratory Narrative: Let Users Discover the Easter Egg</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">An ad clearly tells you "our product is great" — you scroll past. Something that makes you discover it yourself creates 3× more trust than being told.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201918==z--探索式叙事__chapter14__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C14</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Open Source Project Narrative: Let Code Tell Its Own Story</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Great code is just the entry fee. What makes a project actually get used is narrative — the difference between a 3-line and 300-line README isn't word count.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--开源项目叙事__chapter20__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C15</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Narrative Leadership: From "I" to "We"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Why can some people drive change while others can't? The difference isn't power — it's the ability to tell a story people want to follow.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--叙事领导力__chapter22__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Part 3: AI-Era Narrative Mastery (C16 ~ C21)</h2>
      <div class="chapter-list">

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C16</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Meta-Skill: Turn Narrative Methods Into AI-Executable Instructions</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">The narrative methods in your head — AI can't understand them. Translating methods into Prompts is the core competitive skill of AI-era storytellers.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--元Skill__chapter15__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C17</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Narrative Memory: Build Your Storytelling Asset Library</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Inspiration that's not recorded disappears. Turn scattered thoughts, cases, and quotes into searchable, reusable narrative assets.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--叙事记忆库__chapter16__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C18</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">De-AI-ing: Keep the "Human Touch" in AI-Assisted Narrative</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">AI-written content is always "差不多." De-AI-ing means preserving the authentic details and emotions that only humans can create, on top of AI-generated drafts.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--去AI化__chapter17__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C19</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Human-AI Collaboration: From Fragment to Published</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">idea → AI draft → human refinement → publish → iterate — a repeatable workflow that makes AI an amplifier, not a replacement.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--人机协作工作流__chapter18__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C20</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Personal IP: Turn Your Resume Into a Story</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Open your LinkedIn or WeChat bio. Do you write "XX Company Founder" or "Why I built this"? The former is a resume. The latter is a story.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--个人IP__chapter19__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C21</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">Continuous Evolution of Narrative Skill</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">Narrative skill isn't learned once and done — it's a continuously iterating system. From deliberate practice to intuitive mastery, the path to narrative freedom.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--叙事技能的持续进化__chapter21__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">Book →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">All Chapters on GitHub</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 16px;">Complete book (Chinese + English notes) available on GitHub. Source files in .org format.</p>
      <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/tree/main/chapters/book" target="_blank" class="cta">View All Chapters →</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .chapter-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .chapter-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: white;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .chapter-item:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .chapter-main { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; flex: 1; }
  .chapter-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    min-width: 50px;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .chapter-body { flex: 1; }
  .chapter-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .chapter-desc { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .chapter-versions { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .chapter-link {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 3px 12px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .chapter-link:hover { background: var(--accent); color: white; }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .chapter-item { flex-direction: column; }
    .chapter-versions { align-self: flex-end; }
  }
</style>
